responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "7A8FDF12488F69CF07B70C9C108479ED", "Broken? Surely grounds for inquiry as a deserter. The Major is really going to grill me for this, and I doubt they\'ll issue a new one anytime soon. Most likely, they\'ll add an extra heaping of goblin duty to really test my mettle. Still, it\'s a good thing you passed through when you did. I\'m grateful that you\'ve saved me some trouble.")
